Build me a private job-search automation system for Keandra Morris with a review dashboard.

MAIN GOAL
Create a private automation system that scans for remote full-time jobs, scores each job against my background, drafts a tailored resume and cover letter, and loads everything into a dashboard where I can review, approve, reject, or self-apply.

The system must NOT apply to jobs automatically until I approve. For MVP, focus on job discovery, filtering, scoring, document drafting, and dashboard review.

