JOB SCORING SYSTEM
Score each job from 0–100:
- Title alignment: 20 points
- Salary alignment: 20 points
- Remote eligibility: 15 points
- Experience match: 20 points
- Skill match: 15 points
- Growth/path value: 10 points

Labels:
- Green Light: 80–100
- Yellow Light: 65–79
- Red Light: below 65 or failed hard filter

